{"title":"拆解最新Figma Motion：0门槛用AI制作高级动效","slug":"brg1h2p0uzdnxfp1","summary":"作为一名天天和 Figma 打交道的 UI/UX 设计师，看完 Config 2026 大会关于 Figma Motion 的发布，抓紧去体验了一下。不得不说，这次 Figma 确实憋了个大招，直接把动效变成了画布上的“一等公民”。 过去我们为了做个高保真动效，要在 Figma、","category":"8. 用AI做动效设计","tags":["PART7️⃣ 设计全流程AI提效指南","8. 用AI做动效设计"],"featured":false,"order":116,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-06-27","wordCount":1326,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/brg1h2p0uzdnxfp1","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"u9407cc8a\" id=\"u9407cc8a\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud1c6f5a7\" id=\"ud1c6f5a7\">作为一名天天和 Figma 打交道的 UI/UX 设计师，看完 Config 2026 大会关于 Figma Motion 的发布，抓紧去体验了一下。不得不说，这次 Figma 确实憋了个大招，直接把动效变成了画布上的“一等公民”。<br />过去我们为了做个高保真动效，要在 Figma、After Effects、Protopie 甚至浏览器插件之间疯狂切换，切图切到吐，改个需求全流程重来。但现在，Figma Motion 直接在画布里塞进了一条原生时间轴（Timeline）。<br />在深度体验了一把之后，我连夜整理了这份设计师视角的超详细上手攻略与心得，带大家看看这个新功能到底怎么玩，又会如何改变我们的工作流。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ua4d9b654\" id=\"ua4d9b654\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1782570846256-595eb062-f39a-477c-8920-e4be796c0be0.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u313ab20a-cdf1-4357-a636-182d03efcc7%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf63aae80-71c4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A540%2C%22height%22%3A405%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22Mask%20group.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A687164%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A810%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22CREN%20CANYON%20HEETUP%201.4%200.6%201.2%200.4%201%200.8%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A636%2C%22y%22%3A77%2C%22width%22%3A342%2C%22height%22%3A152%2C%22text%22%3A%22CREN%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A65%2C%22y%22%3A80%2C%22width%22%3A488%2C%22height%22%3A149%2C%22text%22%3A%22CANYON%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A271%2C%22y%22%3A240%2C%22width%22%3A476%2C%22height%22%3A150%2C%22text%22%3A%22HEETUP%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1008%2C%22y%22%3A563%2C%22