）。你可以直接把动效链接丢给像 Claude Code 这样的 AI 编程代理，AI 能完美读取动画上下文，吐出来的代码和你的设计意图零误差。</span></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u66155dc6\" id=\"u66155dc6\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1782570912860-e3c479c4-0dc2-409d-9b6b-b29a651fe998.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ubfc54ff5-a8ca-4a1e-a825-860a9018973%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf63aae80-71c4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A600%2C%22height%22%3A311%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image%20382.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A176743%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1200%2C%22originHeight%22%3A622%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22MOTION%209%3A41%20CODE%20CSS%20LIST%20SEARCH%20ANIMATION%20TECHNOLOGY%20ALL%20FASHION%20SOUNC%20BIO%20ART%20STYLE%20ANIMATION%3A%20ROTATE_1%202S%3B%20KEYFRAMES%20%40KEYFRAMES%20ROTATE_1%20%7B%201234%200%25%20ROTATE(0DEG)%3B%20%7D%20Y%20TRANSFORM%3A%20ROTATE(360DEG)%3B%20%7D%20100%25%20TRANSFORM%3A%20%E5%AD%90%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A580%2C%22y%22%3A30%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22MOTION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A130%2C%22y%22%3A93%2C%22width%22%3A34%2C%22height%22%3A16%2C%22text%22%3A%229%3A41%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A690%2C%22y%22%3A95%2C%22width%22%3A57%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22CODE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1074%2C%22y%22%3A93%2C%22width%22%3A46%2C%22height%22%3A23%2C%22text%22%3A%22CSS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A607%2C%22y%22%3A96%2C%22width%22%3A41%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22LIST%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A138%2C%22y%22%3A161%2C%22width%22%3A54%2C%22height%22%3A15%2C%22text%22%3A%22SEARCH%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A581%2C%22y%22%3A173%2C%22width%22%3A109%2C%22height%22%3A20%2C%22text%22%3A%22ANIMATION%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A155%2C%22y%22%3A221%2C%22width%22%3A77%2C%22height%22%3A18%2C%22text%22%3A%22TECHNOLOGY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A100%2C%22y%22%3A221%2C%22width%22%3A20