%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6118d5fe%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"iVPoG\" id=\"iVPoG\"><span data-lake-id=\"ua70a0231\" id=\"ua70a0231\">💡</span><span data-lake-id=\"uedc83d42\" id=\"uedc83d42\"> 个人体验总结与心得</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u8b625aa5\" id=\"u8b625aa5\"><span data-lake-id=\"uf320a59b\" id=\"uf320a59b\">体验完 Figma Motion 之后，我的第一感受是：“原子化设计”正式进化成了“原子化动效设计”。<br />过去，动效往往是产品设计的“最后一步”或是“锦上添花”的奢侈品，因为团队总会担心它影响开发进度或增加落地风险。但现在，Figma 把动效拉到了产品设计的起点，从你画下第一个原型开始，它就是有生命力的。<br />墙裂建议大家去看看Playground操练文件，你会瞬间打开新世界的大门！</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u1b953374\" id=\"u1b953374\"><a href=\"https://www.figma.com/community/file/1647513942386018246\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u547c1a4d\" id=\"u547c1a4d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u79d406ef\" id=\"u79d406ef\">https://www.figma.com/community/file/1647513942386018246</span></a></p><p data-lake-id=\"u77a91f71\" id=\"u77a91f71\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1782570920682-7db2f4cf-e12e-4c34-bcb6-5d28939097a1.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ucf2346f3-0d7d-40d9-b0dc-0322a2ea40f%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22uf63aae80-71c4-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A600%2C%22height%22%3A304%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22%E6%88%AA%E5%B1%8F2026-06-27%2022.03.52%201.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A147015%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1200%2C%22originHeight%22%3A608%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22EDUCATION%3E%20DESIGN%20TUTORIALS%20MORTH%20FIGMA%20COMMUNITY%20CONFIG%202026%20CONFIG%202026%20PLAYGROUND%20355%5C%22%20PLAYGROUND%20DESIGN%20FILE%60218%20218.9K%20USERS%20GET%20UP%20TO%20SPEED%20ON%20SOME%20OF%20OUR%20BIGGEST%20%E5%8F%A3%20OPEN%20IN%20FIGMA%20LAUNCHES%20FROM%20CONFIG%20%202026.%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A57%2C%22y%22%3A29%2C%22width%22%3A182%2C%22height%22%3A1